title: The Saints-A Concise Biographical Dictionary (History Religion)
description:
The Saints: A Concise Biographical Dictionary
Hawthorn Books | 1958 | English | 536 pages | PDF | 72.7 MB

Here is a completely new one-volume lives of the saints which is both authoritative in its research and exciting in its writing and illustration. Not the work of a single scholar, but rather the product of a distinguished galaxy of theologians and Bible scholars as well as historians, scientists and even novelists and psychiatrists, these differing outlooks and approaches, united in a common Faith, combine to produce a lively and stimulating work - a book to browse in and to discuss as well as a major work of reference
